Developed a To-Do List application using Tkinter, incorporating a modern and user-friendly interface with enhanced background colors and button styles for improved usability.
Implemented task addition, deletion, and completion marking functionalities, allowing users to manage their tasks efficiently.
Designed a responsive entry window for adding new tasks, featuring dynamic warning messages to ensure input validation.
Optimized task display with a scrollable listbox, ensuring smooth navigation through tasks using integrated scrollbar support.
Enhanced user experience by toggling task completion status visually, enabling clear differentiation between completed and pending tasks with dynamic updates.
